THIS  Projeect consists Pico Peripheral programs , but thay are build to  Run IN SRAM  using the  (no_flash) macro in cmake . If you  want to flash the program into  flash memory  disable the following linw in  your cmake - pico_set_binary_type(${PROJECT}  no_flash)

use this Picotool command to upload to sram -  picotool load -u -v -x -t elf  filename .elf    
